Here is my Zephyr blackbird sr-71 inspired long-range plane:

> [Javascript is disabled. View full album](//imgur.com/a/sKgye)

I thought about what a kerbal would think of the blackbird and this was the result.

Compatible with AJE (that's why it has so many intakes) and FAR, it should work with stock (tell me if it doesn't).

Instructions:

1 Stage drop tanks when empty.

2 Brakes activate spoiler

3 ?

4 Science!

Enjoy!
